This paper deals with building a ranking system for entities using knowledge bases, which involves information retrieval (IR) techniques. Additionally, the use of multiple languages and the reliance on large datasets suggest that this work could also fall under the categories of computational linguistics (CL), databases (DB), artificial intelligence (AI), and machine learning (LG).
